originalTranscription: My name is Silas, and I'm in L2, and I love Alpha because I get to learn four times your amount of material in three months. I, you get to learn at your own pace, and it's complete at your own pace because in my last school, it was like I was often waiting for a lot of people to finish the subject. I love Alpha because there's no hand holding, and I get to learn at my own pace.
